Josh Vine Age 37

Davenport, IA

Josh Vine lives in Davenport, IA. He is a 2001 graduate of North High School and 2005 graduate of Kaplan College. He has worked for Target, Web Design, Assistant Manager, Meat, Video Games Etc. and Web Designretail. Josh's a big fan of Television. Anchorman, Family Guy, Dawn Of The Dead and Night Of The Living Dead are among his all-time favorite films.

Josh D. Vine Age 37

Littleton, CO | Loveland, CO

Josh Vine lives in Littleton, CO. He has also lived in Loveland, CO. He attended the The University Of Texas At El Paso, Arapahoe Community College, Western State College Of Colorado and Dakota Ridge Senior High School. His favorite bands are Incubus, Atreyu, Thrice, Tool, Rancid, Weezer, Nirvana, Deftones, Nonpoint, Tim Mcgraw, Green Day, Smashing Pumpkins, Avenged Sevenfold, Norma Jean, Black Sabbath, Pearl Jam, Stone Temple Pilots, Nine Inch Nails, A Perfect Circle, Social Distortion, Flogging Molly, Tiger Army, Maroon 5, Phantom Planet, The Transplants, Authority Zero, Dropkick Murphys, A Static Lullaby, Red Hot Chili Peppers, Dashboard Confessional and Linkin Park. Gladiator, Trainspotting, Mallrats, Scarface, The Boondock Saints, Chasing Amy, The Program, Reservoir Dogs, The Big Lebowski, Half Baked, Black Hawk Down, Good Will Hunting, 8 Seconds, The Longest Yard, Good Fellas, Death By Stereo, Lock, Stock & Two Smoking Barrels, Kill Bill Movies and The Hangover are some of the films he loves.
